# Implement Xvideos Tool

## Goal
Add a comprehensive Xvideos tool containing "Download" (from URL) and "Search" (by keyword) functionalities.

## Architecture
`Frontend` -> `Cloudflare Function` -> `n8n Webhook` -> `External API (api.satoru.click)`

## Components

### 1. n8n Workflow (`Xvideos API.json`)
- **Trigger**: Webhook POST `/xvideos`
- **Logic**: Switch node based on `body.action`:
    - Case [download](file:///i:/Workflow/n8n/Workflow/Backups/web-fontend-v2/src/components/ShortenForm.tsx#58-85): GET `https://api.satoru.click/api/xvideos/download?url={url}`
    - Case `search`: GET `https://api.satoru.click/api/xvideos?q={query}`
- **Response**: JSON result.

### 2. Cloudflare Function ([functions/api/xvideos.ts](file:///i:/Workflow/n8n/Workflow/Backups/web-fontend-v2/functions/api/xvideos.ts))
- Proxy to n8n webhook defined in `N8N_XVIDEOS_WEBHOOK_URL`.

### 3. Frontend Component ([src/components/XvideosDownload.tsx](file:///i:/Workflow/n8n/Workflow/Backups/web-fontend-v2/src/components/XvideosDownload.tsx))
- **State**: `mode` ('download' | 'search').
- **UI - Download Mode**:
    - Input URL.
    - Result: Title, Thumbnail, Video Player (if possible), Download Buttons (Low/High).
- **UI - Search Mode**:
    - Input Keyword.
    - Grid Result: Thumbnails, Titles, Duration.
    - Interaction: Clicking a result switches to Download mode or directly fetches download links.

### 4. App Integration ([src/App.tsx](file:///i:/Workflow/n8n/Workflow/Backups/web-fontend-v2/src/App.tsx))
- Add "Xvideos" to the Tool Switcher.

# Implement SoundCloud Tool

## Goal
Add SoundCloud music downloader tool.

## Architecture
`Frontend` -> `Cloudflare Function` -> `n8n Webhook` -> `External API (api.satoru.click)`

## Components

### 1. n8n Workflow (`SoundCloud Download API.json`)
- **Trigger**: Webhook POST `/soundcloud`
- **Action**: GET `https://api.satoru.click/api/soundcloud/download?url={url}`
- **Response**: JSON result (Track info + Download links).

### 2. Cloudflare Function ([functions/api/soundcloud.ts](file:///i:/Workflow/n8n/Workflow/Backups/web-fontend-v2/functions/api/soundcloud.ts))
- Proxy to n8n webhook defined in `N8N_SOUNDCLOUD_WEBHOOK_URL`.

### 3. Frontend Component ([src/components/SoundCloudDownload.tsx](file:///i:/Workflow/n8n/Workflow/Backups/web-fontend-v2/src/components/SoundCloudDownload.tsx))
- Input URL.
- Display Track Info: Artwork, Title, Artist, Plays/Likes stats.
- Download Buttons: Filter `download_links` for `progressive` (MP3) or valid audio streams.

### 4. App Integration ([src/App.tsx](file:///i:/Workflow/n8n/Workflow/Backups/web-fontend-v2/src/App.tsx))
- Add "SoundCloud" tab between "Zing MP3" and "Xvideos".

## Dependencies
- Lucide icons (`Music`, `Headphones`, etc.)

# Mobile Optimization

## Goal
Optimize layout for mobile devices to fix clutter and improve UX.

## Changes

### 1. [src/components/Header.tsx](file:///i:/Workflow/n8n/Workflow/Backups/web-fontend-v2/src/components/Header.tsx)
- **Layout**: Change from `flex-col` to `flex-row` on mobile.
- **Hamburger Menu**: Add `Menu` icon for mobile.
- **Mobile Drawer**: Slide-out menu containing Navigation, Language, and Theme controls.
- **Logo**: Adjust font size for mobile.

### 2. [src/App.tsx](file:///i:/Workflow/n8n/Workflow/Backups/web-fontend-v2/src/App.tsx)
- **Tool Switcher**: Convert to horizontal scrollable list (`overflow-x-auto`) on mobile to prevent wrapping/stacking.
- **Typography**: Reduce main title size on mobile (`text-3xl` -> `text-2xl`).


## Dependencies
- `react-player` (optional, or just use native `<video>`).
- Existing `lucide-react` icons.

